    "For some time, developments in AI have been viewed by researchers as promising avenues for the increasingly complex OCCF detection problem.",
    "At the time of writing, a Google Scholar search using simple keywords online credit card fraud detection+machine learning returns 17,000 related publications since 2018.",
    "Traditional rule-based Machine Learning (ML), Deep Learning (DL) and Ensemble Learning (EL) feature extensively in the returned results and are of particular interest to this paper.",
